        <font color="white" face="Verdana" size="2"> Hi,</P><P>I am new to th world of the necromancer (i have barely started) and i was trying to find a guide for the Erudite Necromancer.  I have found some guide for the begining Dark elves and gnomes follower of the dark art, but nothing specific for the Erudite.</P><P>I would like to know what quest are available near my starting town, and what/where should i hunt when i am too old for the newbie grounds</P><P>thanks</P><P><BR> </font></td>

