        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         I advise against doing any quests in Paineel.  When you start out, you can make it through Erudin without being KOS (or at least you used to).  If you do any quests, you'll ruin your already tenuous faction.</P><P>IMO, the quests really aren't worth the faction hits.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
