        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         About Erudites and Neriak faction...</P><P>You will be accepted (barely) in Neriak, but I don't know that they'll do business with you.  My little Erudite Necro went to Neriak to find some spells, and all was well until I got to the Necro/SK guild.  The ghouls outside attacked, and all the guards between there and the zoneline joined in.  So beware of those guys... I guess they look at the foreheads as competition or something...</P><P>Good luck!</P><P>Death is your friend.  Introduce everyone you meet.<BR><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
