         In Neriak just remember to cast IvU before you run into the guild and once more before you head out and you are fine. As for the Molars, go ahead and turn them in unless you have some reason to go to the Clerics and Caster guild in Erudin, the path to the docks don't take you in contact with them. heck I am Warmly in Paineel and Ally in Erudin (go figure).  Just remember you start off KoS in Qeynos so Gather Shadows or running through the sewers is your friend.</P><P>Kekhet Shadowshott<BR>56 Defiler<BR>Virtute et Armis<BR>Seventh Hammer<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
