         Ok, the ghouls will attack.  Next question: has anyone tried Invis to Undead to get inside?  Once inside can we do business with the trainers there?  </P><P>Next question: Are the ghouls on the same faction as the Neriak necromancers?  If they are, can you kill mobs/do quests to improve your faction with the necro guild (The Dead they're called, I think) to make it so you're not KOS to the ghouls?</P><P>If the ghouls are in fact on the Dead faction, then I'm gonna assume that the trainers would be KOS to us as well.  </P><P>Last question (gads, I'm fulla questions, ain't I?) has anyone found necro trainers/places to buy spells on the moon?  I've checked EQAtlas, and perhaps I'm just missing it, but I don't see anyplace on Luclin for us to train.</P><P>Toxi<BR>Lvl 15 Necromancer<BR>Terris Thule<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
